Like Lash, I was not impressed with the interserver class channels.  It was mostly &quot;well on Sullon Zek, we can kick anyone's butt unlike the people on those 'carebear' servers&quot; or something to that extent.<br>
<br>
Oh for a quick reference so you don't have to go link hopping:<br>
<br>
;tell antonius.alhazro  -  sends Alhazro on AB a message<br>
<br>
/join serverwide.bards  -  lets you into the interserver bard channel<br>
<br>
